title: Mike Doughty Discography, February 2014
description:
I noticed there wasn't any good Mike Doughty Discographies out there so I thought I would throw one together. It contains all studio and live albums so far that I am aware of.

2002 Smofe + Smang: Live In Minneapolis
2004 Skittish/Rockity Roll
2005 Haughty Melodic
2008 Golden Delicious
2009 Sad Man Happy Man
2011 Dubious Luxury
2011 Yes and Also Yes
2012 The Question Jar Show
2012 The Flip is Another Honey
2012 The Lo-Fi Lodge
2013 Water & Washington
2013 Circles Super Bon Bon

Most mp3s are 256 and 320 kbps with some of them being 190 VBR. They all sound good on my equipment. All mp3s have been correctly tagged including album artwork.

If you enjoy Mike's music head over to his website and buy it or get tickets for a show.
